document_data.DDEX3-01 - Harried in Hillsfar:
{{main|Harried in Hillsfar}}

{{Quote|''In the village of Elventree, near the oppressive city of Hillsfar, a recent string of strange occurrences has the locals on edge. The factions have gathered here on the borders of the forest of Cormanthor to determine what's happening. Is this the machinations of Hillsfar, or something more? Five one-hour mini-adventures for 1st–2nd level characters.''|}}

* '''Designer(s):''' [[Shawn Merwin]]
* '''Editor(s):''' [[Claire Hoffman]], [[Chris Tulach]], [[Travis Woodall]]
* '''Debut:''' July 30, 2015 (Gen Con Indy)
* '''Released:''' September 1, 2015
* '''Playing Time:''' 5 hours
* '''Levels:''' 1{{st}} – 2{{nd}}
* '''Setting:''' [[Hillsfar]], [[Cormanthor]], [[Elventree]]

document_data.DDEX3-02 - Shackles of Blood:
{{main|Shackles of Blood}}

{{Quote|''The Red Plumes have increased patrols in the region surrounding Hillsfar, and a string of disappearances has followed in their wake. Naturally, this has roused the suspicion of the factions. Join your factions and find out the truth behind the missing farmers.''|}}

