document_data.DDEX3-15 - Szith Morcane Unbound:
{{main|Szith Morcane Unbound}}

{{Quote|''With allies gained from denizens of the Underdark, the former drow enclave of Szith Morcane is on the precipice of being retaken. During the battle for Szith Morcane, secrets of the drow community are revealed. What will you do with this knowledge, and how will it affect the outcome of the conflict?''|}}

